{"id":13587,"date":"2020-12-02T10:50:30","date_gmt":"2020-12-02T09:50:30","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/?page_id=13587"},"modified":"2023-11-15T13:16:14","modified_gmt":"2023-11-15T12:16:14","slug":"diversity-and-inclusion","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/en\/career\/working-at-mannheimer-swartling\/diversity-and-inclusion\/","title":{"rendered":"Diversity and inclusion"},"content":{"rendered":"<p class=\"preamble\">Like everyone else in the legal industry, we face a diversity challenge. Many of Sweden\u2019s most promising young lawyers apply to join the firm, and most of the best candidates are women. We therefore recruit more female lawyers than male and yet, historically, fewer female lawyers have become partners.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-22665 size-medium\" src=\"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/app\/uploads\/2022\/11\/00-corporate-127-1200x778.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1200\" height=\"778\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/app\/uploads\/2022\/11\/00-corporate-127-1200x778.jpg 1200w, https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/app\/uploads\/2022\/11\/00-corporate-127-2000x1297.jpg 2000w, https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/app\/uploads\/2022\/11\/00-corporate-127-800x519.jpg 800w, https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/app\/uploads\/2022\/11\/00-corporate-127-768x498.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/app\/uploads\/2022\/11\/00-corporate-127-1536x996.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/app\/uploads\/2022\/11\/00-corporate-127-2048x1328.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Inclusiveness is not merely quantitative gender equality or equal opportunities. The challenge is not just to find people who \u201cfit in\u201d, but to create a workplace and a culture that foster the potential of all our employees and encourage them to remain with the firm to an equal extent. This of course applies not just to gender, but to all aspects of diversity.<\/p>\n<p>We cannot pat ourselves on the back and say we have achieved our goal, because we haven\u2019t \u2013 not yet. What we can say is that we are working hard on this issue every day, in all parts of our business. Below are some examples of our approach to inclusiveness and diversity.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Like everyone else in the legal industry, we face a diversity challenge. Many of Sweden\u2019s most promising young lawyers apply to join the firm, and\u2026<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":5,"featured_media":0,"parent":13574,"menu_order":2,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-13587","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"acf":[],"lang":"en","translations":{"en":13587,"sv":8802},"pll_sync_post":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/13587"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/5"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=13587"}],"version-history":[{"count":15,"href":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/13587\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":26160,"href":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/13587\/revisions\/26160"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/13574"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=13587"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}